		<div class="featurewrapper">
			<p>With Nextcloud 9.0, you can seamlessly collaborate on files and folders with others, <em>add comments</em> while working on files and <em>organize files via tags</em>. Keep an eye on what happens to your files through the <em>activity feed</em>, available in the Activity app, through RSS or in the Nextcloud client apps. <em>Notifications</em> will pop up with calendar invitations or when files are shared. The Nextcloud community developed a wide variety of applications bringing additional collaborative capabilities like email handling, calendar and contacts, and more.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="row featurerow">
			<div class="col-md-6 featureblock">
